# NeoVision Component Patterns

## 1. 氛围光晕 `.glow-orb`

页面背景必须有 3 个固定定位的巨大模糊圆形：

```css
.glow-orb {
  position: fixed;
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(140px);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}
.glow-orb.a { width:600px; height:600px; top:-200px; left:-150px; background:var(--glow-a); }
.glow-orb.b { width:500px; height:500px; top:60vh; right:-180px; background:var(--glow-b); }
.glow-orb.c { width:400px; height:400px; top:120vh; left:30%; background:var(--glow-c); }
```

**规则：**
- 必须放在 `<body>` 最顶部，所有内容之前
- z-index 必须为 0
- pointer-events 必须为 none
- 光晕颜色用 var(--glow-a/b/c)，不要硬编码

## 2. 导航 `.nav`

```css
.nav {
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%);
  background: var(--nav-bg);
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
}
.nav-inner {
  max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px;
  height: 56px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
}
```

**子元素：**
- `.nav-logo` — 18px, weight 650, letter-spacing -0.3px，`span` 部分用 accent 色
- `.nav-links` — flex 排列，gap 32px，链接 14px weight 450，颜色 text-2，hover 变 text
- `.nav-cta` — 13px weight 550，胶囊按钮：border-radius 100px，背景 surface，边框 border，padding 7px 18px，hover 升级到 border-h
- `.theme-toggle` — 36x36 圆形按钮，sun/moon SVG 图标通过 `[data-theme="light"]` 切换显示

**移动端（≤900px）：** `.nav-links { display: none }`

## 3. 玻璃拟态卡片 `.card`

```css
.card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 28px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.card:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-h);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
}
```

**卡片尺寸类（Bento Grid 专用）：**
- `.card-2x2` — `grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 2`
- `.card-2x1` — `grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 1`
- `.card-1x2` — `grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 2`
- `.card-1x1` — `grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1`

**卡片内容结构（从上到下）：**
1. `.card-tag` — 11px weight 550 uppercase，颜色 accent。变体：`.warm`(#e0a870) `.green`(#6ecf8a)
2. `.card-title` — 19px weight 550 letter-spacing -0.3px，`.card-2x2` 内升级为 26px
3. `.card-desc` — 13px text-2，可选
4. `.card-stats` — flex 数据行，`.card-stat-val` 22px weight 600，`.card-stat-label` 12px text-3
5. `.card-meta` — flex + 5px dot(accent色) + text-3 时间文字，12px，放在 margin-top:auto

**大卡片内发光（`.card-2x2`）：**
```css
.card-2x2::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -80px; right: -60px;
  width: 200px; height: 200px;
  background: rgba(120,100,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(60px);
  pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
}
.card-2x2 > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
```

**Hero 卡片变体：**
```css
.card-hero {
  justify-content: flex-end;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--glow-a) 0%, transparent 50%);
}
```

## 4. 新闻卡片 `.news-card`

```css
.news-card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 24px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;
}
.news-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-h);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
}
```

**内容结构：**
- `.news-source` — 11px weight 550 uppercase text-3
- `h3` — 17px weight 530 letter-spacing -0.3px
- `.news-excerpt` — 13px text-2
- `.news-time` — 12px text-3, margin-top:auto

## 5. Footer `.footer`

```css
.footer {
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  padding: 48px 0 32px;
  margin-top: 40px;
}
```

- `.footer-inner` — max-width 1200px, flex, justify-between
- 左：`.footer-brand` + 副标题
- 右：三栏链接 `.footer-col`，每栏有 `.col-title`（11px uppercase text-3）
- `.footer-bottom` — 底部版权，border-top 分割

## 6. 主题切换

```js
// 读取保存的主题
const saved = localStorage.getItem('theme');
if (saved === 'light') {
  document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'light');
}
// 点击切换
toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
  const current = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme');
  const next = current === 'light' ? '' : 'light';
  if (next) {
    document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', next);
    localStorage.setItem('theme', next);
  } else {
    document.documentElement.removeAttribute('data-theme');
    localStorage.removeItem('theme');
  }
});
```

主题属性挂 `<html data-theme="light">`，localStorage key 为 `theme`。
